headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Podium Vehicle: The Grotti Cheetah Classic
content: Swing by the lobby of The Diamond and give the Lucky Wheel a customary spin for the opportunity to walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, myriad mystery prizes and more. This week on the podium is the Grotti Cheetah Classic, a sleek Italian sportscar with the lithe musculature and grace of a gazelle injected with performance enhancing drugs.
